[[Image:Domyojitenmangu syura(fukugen).jpg|thumb|200px|right|Reconstructed ''shura'' from {{ill|Mitsuzuka Kofun|ja|三ツ塚古墳|12=draft|12=draft}} (housed at {{ill|Dōmyōji Tenmangū|ja|道明寺天満宮|12=draft|12=draft}})]] '''Shura''' (修羅) is a large wooden {{ill|sled|ja|橇|12=draft|12=draft}} used for transporting heavy {{ill|stone materials|ja|石材|1=Building Stone|2=ja|3=石材|4=ko|5=석재|6=fr|7=Pierre à bâtir|8=nl|9=Bouwsteen|10=it|11=Pietra (classificazione commerciale)|12=draft|12=draft}}.
